---
title: Turkey Smash Burgers with Burger Sauce and Seasoned Potatoes
description: These turkey smash burgers bring crispy goodness to your stovetop! Crunchy pickles and savoury caramelized onions are served atop an all-turkey patty!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/smash-burgers-a-la-dinde-0c9a7b4b.jpg
